      "raw_text": "CHICAGO, Dec. ~. - Grievance\ncommittees of 40 different railways\nwest Of Chicago, including the Great\nNorthern. Northern Pacific, o. r. &\nN, and others reaching the coast this\nmorning presented demands for 20\nper cent increase in wages. The\nroads answers will come January 5.\nThey represent 1900 passenger and\nfreight conductors and brakemen."
